1. write your program - don't forget git

2. push to remote repo

3. inside your server:

    3.1. install nodejs

    3.2. install npm

    3.4. clone your repo

    3.4. npm i - all your packages

    3.4. start your server

4. for updates:

    4.1 git pull
    4.2 re-run

5. for crushes: use PM2 package - move to background-service and restart the service in case of crush
